OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery showers return to most
OL,6,Fareas on Wednesday, with northern and
OL,7,Feastern areas having the greatest
OL,8,Fchance of hearing some thunder with a
OL,9,Frisk of hail too. Some pleasant sunny
OL,10,Fspells are likely, especially through
OL,11,Fthe afternoon, feeling rather cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning dry for a time
OL,14,Fovernight with clear skies. However,
OL,15,Flow cloud and rain arrives in the west
OL,16,Fthrough the early hours. Turning
OL,17,Fmilder in the west, chilly elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
