OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet and rather windy day
OL,6,Fas rain spreads across east, turning
OL,7,Flocally heavy at times, but easing
OL,8,Flater. Feeling muggy under widespread
OL,9,Fcloud cover. Turning drier by the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
